(33, 'http://news.rpi.edu/update.do?artcenterkey=2852', 'http://news.rpi.edu/update.do?artcenterkey=2852', 'Rensselaer Professor Xuegang (Jeff) Ban Receives NSF CAREER Award', '\nXuegang (Jeff) Ban, assistant professor in the Department of Civil and Environmental Engineering at Rensselaer, has won a prestigious Faculty Early Career Development Award (CAREER) from the National Science Foundation (NSF).    ', '2011-04-11 03:14:00'),
(34, 'http://events.rpi.edu:80/event/eventView.do?calPath=%2Fpublic%2Fcals%2FMainCal&guid=CAL-00f18254-2abb0f2d-012b-7ec46a22-000058c5calendars@rpi.edu&recurrenceId=', 'http://events.rpi.edu:80/event/eventView.do?calPath=%2Fpublic%2Fcals%2FMainCal&guid=CAL-00f18254-2abb0f2d-012b-7ec46a22-000058c5calendars@rpi.edu&recurrenceId=', 'Banner Production System Outage Scheduled for April 19', '\nTuesday,        April 19, 2011 5:00 PM          -        7:00 PM                                  Where: Campus-wide                                   Description: The Banner Production system will be unavailable from 5pm until 7pm on Tuesday, April 19th for system maintenance. Systems unavailable during this outage include Banner, SIS, RSS, EARS, WPIQ, BOSSCARS, OSCAR, AppWorx and Nolij. The Data Warehouse will be available with data as of close of business Monday, April 18th.                                  Contact: Integrated Administrative Computing Solutions (IACS) 518-276-6278', '2011-04-11 01:45:03'),
